Subject: [PATCH] configd: Add systemd service file

Since we don't like webos-initscripts approach too much.

Signed-off-by: Herman van Hazendonk <github.com@herrie.org>
---
 files/systemd/configd.service | 34 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 34 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 files/systemd/configd.service

diff --git a/files/systemd/configd.service b/files/systemd/configd.service
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..a9272a9
--- /dev/null
+++ b/files/systemd/configd.service
